title: QuickLoad v3.6 Installer + v3.8 Database Update
description:
QUICKLOAD v3.6 INSTALLER + v3.8 DATABASE UPDATE


1. Download and extract quickload_v3.6 + v3.8 update.zip.

2. Burn QuickLoad 3.6.iso to CD and use CD to install.

3. Burn quickload_v3.8_database_update.iso to CD and use CD to install update.


Notes: 

You must install from CD or virtual CD (magicISO, etc).

If you like program, purchase to help support developer.

Developer website: www.neconos.com/details3.htm

QuickLoad v3.6 installer works on Windows 7
